{{Infobox film awards | number = 5 | award = Best of Nollywood Awards | image = | caption = | date = 5 December 2013 | site = Dome, [[Asaba, Nigeria|Asaba]], [[Delta State|Delta]], [[Nigeria]] | host = | producer = | director = | organizer = Best of Nollywood Magazine | best_picture = | most_wins = | most_nominations = | last = [[2012 Best of Nollywood Awards|4th]] | next = [[2014 Best of Nollywood Awards|6th]] }}
The 5th [[Best of Nollywood Awards]] was held at Dome, [[Asaba, Nigeria|Asaba]], Delta State on December 5, 2013. Several notable personalities like [[Juliet Ibrahim]], [[Omoni Oboli]] and [[Richard Mofe Damijo]] were in attendance. The Dark Comedy film ''[[Confusion Na Wa]]'' won the category ''Movie of the Year''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bonawards.com/nominees/ |title=BON Awards 2013 Winners |accessdate=21 March 2014 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130928233629/http://www.bonawards.com/nominees/ |archivedate=28 September 2013 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://thenet.ng/2013/09/dayo-amusa-tops-bon-awards-nominees-list-with-11-nods/ | title=Bon Nominee list | accessdate=21 March 2014}}</ref>
