orgivable'' |- ! style="background:#EEDD82; width:50%" | Best Special Effects ! style="background:#EEDD82; width:50%" | Best Actor (Hausa) |- | valign="top" | * '''''Judgment Night''''' * ''Twin Sword'' * ''Mufu Olosa Oko'' | valign="top" | * '''Ali Nuhu (''Wani Hanin'')''' * Zaharadeen Sani (''Halayen'') * As Mati in (''Wani Gari'') * Adam A. Zango (''Martani'') |- ! style="background:#EEDD82; width:50%" | Best Actress (Hausa) ! style="background:#EEDD82; width:50%" | Best Supporting Actor (Hausa) |- | valign="top" | * Hafisat Maryam Booth (''Buduwar'') * Nafisat Abdullahi (''Son Zuciya'') * As Lumi (''bakim Alkala'') * Hadiza Aliyu (''Babban Zaure'') | valign="top" | * Adam A. Zango (''Buduwar'') * Ibrahim Nuhu (Raciyin Zuci'') * Sani Musa Danjo * Sadisu Abba (''Halayen'') |- ! style="background:#EEDD82; width:50%" | Best Supporting Actress (Hausa) ! style="background:#EEDD82; width:50%" | Revelation of the Year (Female) |- | valign="top" | * Fatima Ladan (''Abokina'') * As aunt Salma (''Bakin Alkala'') * Ummi Moh’d (''Halayen'') * Ladidi Fagge (''Son Zuciya'') | valign="top" | * '''Laitan Ogungbeile''' * Tamara Eteimo * Tope Oshoba * Uche Benjamin * Chinwe Isaac * Mimi Orijekwe |- ! style="background:#EEDD82; width:50%" | Revelation of the Year (male) ! style="background:#EEDD82; width:50%" | Movie Journalist of the Year |- | valign="top" | * '''Charles Billion Pius''' * Igoni Archibong * Luclay Misoya * Daniel K Daniel * Walter Anga * Michael Godson | valign="top" | * '''Hafeez Balogun ([[Daily Independent (Lagos)|Daily Independent]])''' * Ben Njoku (Vanguard (Nigeria)|Vanguard) * Wemimo Ogunde (Nollywood Mindspace) * Biodun Kupoluyi (E24/7) |- ! style="background:#EEDD82; width:50%" | Marketer of the Year |- | valign="top" | * '''Divine Touch''' * Alhaji Abudullah Rasak (Corporate Pictures) * Alhaji Kazeem Afolayan * Magic Movies * Royal academy * Akagod Production
