'''Danza Teatro Retazos''' (literally ''bits and pieces'') is a [[Cuba]]n dance company. Created in January 1987 by [[choreographer]] Isabel Bustos Romoleroux. Every April since 1996, Retazos sponsors the International Dance Festival in Urban Landscapes — [[Old Havana]], City in Motion.

==Major works==
* Mujeres
* Carmina Burana
* Las Lunas de Lorca
* Peces en las Manos

