==Reception== {{Video game reviews | GR = 49.19%<ref name=GR>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamerankings.com/ps3/954118-the-punisher-no-mercy/index.html |title=The Punisher: No Mercy for PlayStation 3 |publisher=[[GameRankings]] |accessdate=May 27, 2014}}</ref> | MC = 47/100<ref name=MC/> | 1UP = C−<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.1up.com/reviews/punisher-mercy-review |archive-url=https://archive.is/20140527191246/http://www.1up.com/reviews/punisher-mercy-review |dead-url=yes |archive-date=May 27, 2014 |title=The Punisher: No Mercy Review |last=Watts |first=Steve |date=July 6, 2009 |publisher=[[1UP.com]] |accessdate=May 27, 2014}}</ref> | Destruct = {{Rating|3|10}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.destructoid.com/review-the-punisher-no-mercy-139079.phtml |title=Review: The Punisher: No Mercy |last=Nicholson |first=Brad |date=July 10, 2009 |publisher=[[Destructoid]] |accessdate=May 27, 2014}}</ref> | Edge = {{Rating|3|10}}<ref>{{cite journal |author=Edge staff |title=The Punisher: No Mercy |magazine=[[Edge (magazine)|Edge]] |issue=205 |date=September 2009 |page=96}}</ref> | GRadar = {{Rating|2|5}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesradar.com/the-punisher-no-mercy-review/ |title=The Punisher: No Mercy review |last=Dyer |first=Mitch |date=July 9, 2009 |publisher=[[GamesRadar]] |accessdate=May 27, 2014}}</ref> | GSpot = {{Rating|4.5|10}}<ref name=gamespot>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/the-punisher-no-mercy-review/1900-6213000/ |title=The Punisher: No Mercy Review |last=McShea |first=Tom |date=July 6, 2009 |publisher=GameSpot |accessdate=May 27, 2014}}</ref> | GameZone = {{Rating|5.5|10|score=5.7/10 stars}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamezone.com/reviews/the_punisher_no_mercy_ps3_review |title=The Punisher: No Mercy - PS3 - Review |author=Aceinet |date=July 19, 2009 |publisher=GameZone |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090724014651/http://ps3.gamezone.com/gzreviews/r36583.htm |archivedate=July 24, 2009 |deadurl=no |accessdate=May 27, 2014}}</ref> | IGN = {{Rating|4|10|score=4.2/10 stars}}<ref name=ign/> }} The game holds an aggregated rating of 47 out of 100 at [[Metacritic]],<ref name=MC>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/game/playstation-3/the-punisher-no-mercy |title=The Punisher: No Mercy for PlayStation 3 Reviews |publisher=[[Metacritic]] |accessdate=March 25, 2013}}</ref> and 49.19% at [[GameRankings]].<ref name=GR/>
[[GameSpot]] gave the game a score of 4.5 out of 10, criticizing its short length and difficulty of unlocking.<ref name=gamespot/> [[IGN]] gave it 4.2 out of 10, concluding, "The Punisher: No Mercy is a pretty bad game all around. (...) There's just not really anything to like here, unfortunately."<ref name=ign>{{cite web |url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2009/07/06/the-punisher-no-mercy-review |title=The Punisher: No Mercy Review |last1=Roper |first1=Chris |last2= |first2= |date=July 6, 2009 |publisher=[[IGN]] |accessdate=March 25, 2013}}</ref> ''[[PlayStation Official Magazine - UK|PlayStation Official Magazine]] UK'', however, gave the game 7 out of 10, stating, "It's definitely playable, and a respectable value at a penny under seven quid." The game's highest rating came from The Sixth Axis, which gave the game a score of 8/10, concluding "Its replay value is extremely high, and although you’ll unlikely play it for huge stretches of time a couple of rounds with a few friends is incredibly entertaining."<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.thesixthaxis.com/2009/07/07/review-the-punisher-no-mercy/ |title=Review: The Punisher: No Mercy |author=djhsecondnature |date=July 7, 2009 |publisher=The Sixth Axis |accessdate=May 8, 2010}}</ref>
